config BR2_PACKAGE_SVOX
	bool "svox"
        select BR2_PACKAGE_POPT
	help
          The SVOX Pico engine is a software speech synthesizer for German,
          English (GB and US), Spanish, French and Italian.

          SVOX produces a clear and distinct speech output made possible by
          the use of Hidden Markov Model (HMM) algorithms. 
